Tolong hentikan mereka.

00:25:28.783 --> 00:25:29.863
Oke.

00:25:30.463 --> 00:25:31.543
Hentikan mereka.

00:25:34.783 --> 00:25:35.903
Berhenti.

00:25:47.263 --> 00:25:49.263
Anda tidak perlu pergi ke mana pun.

